@startuml CPP_Classes_Part3
!theme plain

title Construction & Destruction Order

package "Object Lifecycle" {
  
  card Construction [
    **Construction Order:**
    1. Allocate memory
    2. Base constructor
       - Initialize vptr
       - Initialize members
    3. Derived constructor
       - Update vptr
       - Initialize members
    
    Base -> Derived (top to bottom)
  ]
  
  card Destruction [
    **Destruction Order:**
    1. Derived destructor
       - Cleanup derived members
    2. Base destructor
       - Cleanup base members
    3. Free memory
    
    Derived -> Base (bottom to top)
  ]
  
  Construction -right-> Destruction
  
  note bottom of Destruction
    CRITICAL: Base destructor
    MUST be virtual!
  end note
}

@enduml